<body>
    <h1>TextNoter Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <section>
        <h2>Data Collection</h2>
        <p>TextNoter collects only the text you explicitly choose to save through the extension. We collect:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Selected text notes</li>
            <li>Timestamp of note creation</li>
            <li>Source URL (optional)</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section>
        <h2>Data Storage</h2>
        <p>All notes are stored locally in your Chrome browser's storage. No data is transmitted to external servers.</p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
        <h2>User Control</h2>
        <p>You have complete control over your data:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Delete individual notes</li>
            <li>Clear all notes at any time</li>
            <li>Uninstall extension to remove all data</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section>
        <h2>Privacy Commitment</h2>
        <p>We do not:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Sell your data</li>
            <li>Share data with third parties</li>
            <li>Access your notes</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Last Updated: December 2024</p>
    </footer>
</body>
